@startuml state_rag_documents
' State machine — SRS §3.14 FR-RAGK-03, §3.15 FR-EXPV-05..06
' rag_documents.review_status lifecycle.

!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
  BorderColor #555
}
title rag_documents.review_status Lifecycle — SRS §3.14

[*] --> pending_review : Admin or\nExpert Reviewer uploads PDF\n(FR-RAGK-01)

pending_review : Docling parsing\nSection-aware 500-token chunking\nMetadata stored (title, authors,\nyear, DOI, quality_tier, study_design)
pending_review : NOT retrieved during coaching\n(FR-RAGK-03)

pending_review --> reviewed_approved : Expert Reviewer approves\n(FR-EXPV-06)
pending_review --> reviewed_rejected : Expert Reviewer rejects
pending_review --> needs_revision : Expert flags issues

needs_revision --> pending_review : Uploader resubmits

reviewed_approved : Cohere embed-v4\n(1024 Matryoshka dims)\nServer-side BM25 sparse\nDeterministic chunk IDs
reviewed_approved --> indexed : Qdrant upsert\n(papers_rag collection)

indexed : retrieved by RetrievalService\n(hybrid dense+sparse + Rerank 4.0)\nquality_tier weight applied\nrecency boost if year >= 2020
indexed --> [*] : (active corpus member)

reviewed_approved --> deleted : Admin deletes\n(FR-RAGK-09)
indexed --> deleted : Admin deletes\n(re-embed trigger or removal)
reviewed_rejected --> [*]
deleted --> [*]

note right of pending_review
  Auto-ingest sources (FR-RAGK-04):
  PubMed E-utilities (MeSH),
  OpenAlex, Semantic Scholar.
  All new records land here.
end note

note right of indexed
  4-layer corpus architecture:
  L1 SR/MA weight 2.0,
  L2 PEDro ≥5 weight 1.5,
  L3 PEDro 3–4 weight 1.0,
  L4 guidelines weight 0.5.
end note

@enduml
